WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.590
It's a small window, but we'll

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.030
take it. It's a small window by

00:00:05.030 --> 00:00:05.040
a

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:07.870
few votes, by a fraction of a hair. I

00:00:07.880 --> 00:00:09.670
see fear in their hearts. I'm seeing it

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:12.030
prophetically. We work on those hearts.

00:00:12.040 --> 00:00:13.830
They're just there. It's just a few

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:16.830
people. The Lord

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:19.030
said, "I'd give you a few. You pray

00:00:19.040 --> 00:00:20.550
over those just right there."He said,

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:21.910
"You see that group right there? I see

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:23.470
them. It's a huddle. It's just

00:00:23.470 --> 00:00:23.480
a

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:25.590
few."One,

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:26.590
two,

00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:29.990
three. I'm counting their faces: four,

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:30.990
five,

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.429
six,

00:00:32.439 --> 00:00:34.150
seven.

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:39.830
And then there's one predominant one.

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:48.830
Pray over these few. The Senate voted 60

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:51.550
to 40 to back a revamp of the GOP funding

00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:53.510
bill that would keep the government open

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:55.430
until the end of January. Eight

00:00:55.440 --> 00:00:57.350
Democrats joined Republicans to pass the

00:00:57.360 --> 00:00:59.430
bill, including Senate Minority Whip Dick

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:01.830
Durbin, Senators Tim Kaine,

00:01:01.830 --> 00:01:01.840
Kathryn

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:04.790
Cortez Masto, and Jacky Rosen, among

00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:07.830
others. A seed on their minds. It's

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:11.430
pressure from the outside. It's pressure

00:01:11.440 --> 00:01:13.190
on them to make this decision.

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.550
"You do what we tell you to

00:01:15.550 --> 00:01:15.560
do."I

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:18.190
hear it.

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:20.070
There's pressure, but it's about

00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:21.310
money.

00:01:21.320 --> 00:01:24.870
"You do what we tell you to do or

00:01:24.870 --> 00:01:24.880
we

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:26.670
cut off the money. Your election

00:01:26.670 --> 00:01:26.680
is

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:29.030
coming up next

00:01:29.030 --> 00:01:29.040
year."I

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:32.190
see the plan. I see

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:33.470
fires.

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:35.430
If we can just get them to flip right

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:36.950
there,

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:38.910
it will be over.

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:40.990
These people

00:01:40.990 --> 00:01:41.000
are

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.190
not too far from it; they're

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:45.470
right on the edge. But they're being

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:48.670
pushed by these other outside sources

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:51.310
and they're being told, "You do what we

00:01:51.320 --> 00:01:54.030
tell you to

00:01:54.040 --> 00:01:56.750
do."Great

00:01:56.760 --> 00:01:59.390
influence is on them for pressure

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:02.670
from their party, but they're so close.

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:06.030
It's by a hair.

00:02:06.030 --> 00:02:06.040
We

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:07.870
just have to push

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:09.310
it over

00:02:09.320 --> 00:02:12.470
by the spirit right now. We call it in

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:14.470
as they're sleeping,

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:17.870
as the Lord is working on their hearts.

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:20.230
At the midnight hour,

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:22.110
we call a turnaround.

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:24.910
We

00:02:24.920 --> 00:02:27.910
call a turnaround over their hearts:

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:30.510
a fear of the

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:34.190
Lord, a sensible budget, a sensible

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:36.670
coming to the table. We're calling it in

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:38.910
right now in Jesus'name. We will not have

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:41.150
riots in this nation. You'll not burn

00:02:41.160 --> 00:02:43.830
our buildings. You'll not steal from us.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:46.190
They'll not have all this

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:49.870
chaos. We call peace over this nation in

00:02:49.880 --> 00:02:53.030
the name of Jesus. We'll have peace over

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:55.790
this nation, over every state: over

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:59.070
Arkansas, over Oklahoma, over

00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:01.590
Texas. I see

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:04.350
even concerning Ukraine.

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:05.630
This money

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:08.830
is for influence in Ukraine.

00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:12.990
Should I say that out loud? Pork.

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:14.470
The arrow

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:19.550
goes from Washington, D.C., into Ukraine

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:22.310
to Kyiv for special

00:03:22.310 --> 00:03:22.320
interests.

00:03:22.320 --> 00:03:25.470
They're trying to protect this,

00:03:25.480 --> 00:03:27.430
but

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:29.950
that money is not accounted for. There's

00:03:29.960 --> 00:03:32.630
no accountability over that money. It

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:35.550
goes in extension to Ukraine and

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:38.430
there's no accountability there.

00:03:38.440 --> 00:03:40.230
You draw your own conclusion. It's

00:03:40.240 --> 00:03:42.310
15

00:03:42.320 --> 00:03:45.790
billion. Is that 15 million? That's a

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:48.350
big number. There is money there. I just

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.790
see the money funneling. Stiff-necked

00:03:50.800 --> 00:03:52.230
people

00:03:52.240 --> 00:03:54.390
with a bad agenda.

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:56.790
Darkness

00:03:56.800 --> 00:04:00.950
in the corners. I see labs,

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:04.870
medical labs,

00:04:04.880 --> 00:04:08.550
science projects.

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:12.430
They look like

00:04:12.440 --> 00:04:13.430
biolabs.

00:04:13.440 --> 00:04:16.229
They have white outfits on and I see

00:04:16.239 --> 00:04:18.390
white counters. Same thing with

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:19.509
Fauci.

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:21.830
Why are they racing so hard?

00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:24.430
It's touching special

00:04:24.430 --> 00:04:24.440
interests,

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:26.990
pet

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:32.150
projects. I'm seeing New Year's Eve

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:37.950
in Times Square. I see

00:04:37.960 --> 00:04:41.030
the two men on CNN. New York

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:42.270
will look so much different at this

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:47.310
time. New York City has elected

00:04:47.310 --> 00:04:47.320
Democratic

00:04:47.320 --> 00:04:50.750
Assemblyman Zohran Mamdani to be its

00:04:50.760 --> 00:04:52.870
next mayor. New York will look so much

00:04:52.880 --> 00:04:55.270
different

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:57.430
by this time.

00:04:57.440 --> 00:05:00.310
It's like no hope for some.

00:05:00.320 --> 00:05:02.190
Sad.

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:05.990
America looks so different in 2026.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.710
There's so much expectation

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:10.510
for the beginning of the new race.

00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:14.870
Every year you're

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:17.150
optimistic. What does this year hold?

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:19.110
You can feel that charge

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:22.430
in the atmosphere. I feel it.

00:05:22.440 --> 00:05:24.910
Everybody wants a blessing; they want

00:05:24.910 --> 00:05:24.920
the

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:33.390
New Year's resolution. They're expecting. I'm in Times Square; I can see it. It's so clear, but I feel a sadness

00:05:33.400 --> 00:05:36.310
there.

00:05:36.310 --> 00:05:36.320
I

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:39.870
see those two men.

00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:41.470
I just camp there, trying to

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.950
figure out why the Lord brought me

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:43.870
there.

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:46.230
Now I'm back in Ukraine.

00:05:49.400 --> 00:05:51.190
I hear John Lennon.

00:05:51.200 --> 00:05:52.830
"Imagine."I

00:05:52.840 --> 00:05:55.430
can hear this song playing.

00:05:55.430 --> 00:05:55.440
"Imagine."Lord,

00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:58.230
Holy Spirit, what

00:05:58.240 --> 00:06:01.710
are you showing me all this for?

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:06.990
"Imagine all the people."It's

00:06:06.990 --> 00:06:07.000
in

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:08.750
New York.

00:06:14.200 --> 00:06:16.350
I just saw a flash. I can see the

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:22.070
building. I hear the people screaming.

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:23.590
Whenever you are in a

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:24.990
crowd, you hear them yelling and

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.950
running. What year is this? I thank

00:06:27.960 --> 00:06:30.390
you, Father, that every plot

00:06:30.390 --> 00:06:30.400
and

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:32.430
every plan

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:35.750
is uncovered in Jesus'name.

00:06:35.750 --> 00:06:35.760
I

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:38.110
plead the blood over my mind.

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:41.830
It looks

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:46.590
like a teardrop,

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:49.870
and the way it goes out

00:06:49.880 --> 00:06:52.750
looks like a teardrop.

00:06:52.750 --> 00:06:52.760
It's

00:06:52.760 --> 00:06:54.790
like

00:06:54.790 --> 00:06:54.800
when

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:56.990
you take a flash on a camera,

00:06:57.000 --> 00:07:00.070
but this is yellow.

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:02.470
It looks like a yellow flash in the

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:03.670
middle,

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:05.750
almost like when you hold a match, but

00:07:05.760 --> 00:07:08.870
this is massive.

00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:08.880
It

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:11.150
goes out

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:14.470
like a flash of light. It moves in

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:16.910
this one area and moves out,

00:07:16.920 --> 00:07:18.550
looking

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:20.790
like fire but shaped

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.990
like a teardrop.

00:07:25.240 --> 00:07:27.910
I hear women

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:30.870
screaming. I can see this move out like

00:07:30.880 --> 00:07:32.110
this.

00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:34.710
It doesn't just go out on the sides;

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:37.150
it goes up and down. A

00:07:37.150 --> 00:07:37.160
flash of

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:41.710
light.

00:07:41.720 --> 00:07:45.270
I see that man's face who is

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:46.870
running for mayor. He

00:07:46.870 --> 00:07:46.880
spoke

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:48.750
before me right then. I see

00:07:48.760 --> 00:07:51.230
his face. I have my assumptions of what

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:52.230
that is.

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:54.150
I'm seeing a little bit more.

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:56.710
To the eagle,

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:02.190
to fatally wound

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:05.270
the eagle. This

00:08:05.270 --> 00:08:05.280
is

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:08.830
the man

00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:10.590
with the black hoodie again. Remember I

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.630
told you?

00:08:11.640 --> 00:08:12.870
It's the

00:08:15.200 --> 00:08:17.910
enemy within.

